110→2. Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web Application)
111→3. Authorized JavaScript origins: `http://localhost:3000`, `https://app.nurge.sh`
112→4. Authorized redirect URIs: `https://<your-deployment>.convex.site/api/auth/callback/google`
113→
