673→```bash
674→npx convex deploy
675→npx convex env set AUTH_GOOGLE_ID <prod-google-client-id> --prod
676→npx convex env set AUTH_GOOGLE_SECRET <prod-google-client-secret> --prod
677→```
678→
679→Update Google Cloud Console redirect URIs to include the production `.convex.site` URL.
