683→## Testing checklist
684→
685→After deploy, verify these work:
686→
687→- [ ] `app.nurge.sh/cli-auth?port=12345&state=test` shows "Sign in with Google"
688→- [ ] After sign-in, redirects to `localhost:12345/callback?code=...&state=test`
689→- [ ] `curl -X POST https://<prod>.convex.site/api/validate-token -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"token":"nrg_bogus"}'` returns `{"valid":false}`
